summary: Full Back and Lower Back Tattoos in the style of my Full Body Tattoos for CBBEv2 Female Bodies.
descriptionHtml:
I received a lot of requests for just the full back tattoos instead of a full body version, (in the same style) so I created these. There are two placements; full back and lower back/buttocks.

Full Back:

Dragon with \"Dragonborn\" text included. (Oblivion style) 

Skull: Giant skull which extends down a bit lower. Suitable for the aspiring Assassin or Necromancer. 

Buddha: It\'s just a design which works really well on the models.

Lower Back/Buttocks:

Butterfly: Moves very smoothly when the model is running.

Fairies: Very small symmetrical design which moves while running; just smaller than the butterfly.

Jolly Roger: Asymmetrical design for the deviant personality. Text says \"No Joy.\" (Oblivion font) The design works a bit better on the skinner models. (very mild distortion at _1)

The \"elven armor,\" in one of the jpegs, if I dare call it that, is a heavily modified version of Killer Keos\' (sp?) versions for the CBBEv2 body. I modified it so when I\'m running the \"full body tattoo\" version of my tattoo textures, I could actually see the majority of the designs while I\'m playing. 

Credit goes to Caliente and Aknot for the body and texture design.
author: Jammer
